txt.en: Many unhatched spider eggs can be found in Taurlingol.\n\nYou should destroy spider egg sacs.

'Those woods are crawling with spiders, aye, but you know what else? Spider eggs! Squash those little devils before they hatch!\n\n'What? Do you think spiders fight fair? Of course not! Deal with them before they become a problem!'
Atli can be found on a hill near Taurlingol.\n\nYou should talk to Atli Spider-bane.
'Did you squish those eggs? Good! One destroyed egg now is one fewer spider later!'
There are many unhatched spider eggs in Taurlingol. Atli suggests you deal with them before they become a problem.
